title: SWP
name: SWP
description:
Southwestern Piñon sampling locations.

Red markers were sampled by Rhett Michelson.  Purple markers were sampled by others and may not have GPS information.

Files including full coordinates for every tree can be found at:
http://research.learnbiology.org/pinyon
